uvicorn (0.35.0-0ubuntu1~ppa1~noble1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial packaging of uvicorn 0.35.0 for the Avalan PPA.
  * Avalan tracks >= 0.35, < 0.36; Debian sid is on 0.38.x (above the
    ceiling) and Noble ships an older 0.27.x, so the rebuild ships
    the pinned 0.35.0 sdist.
  * Core dependencies only (click, h11). The optional `[standard]`
    extra is not declared in the Depends; callers that need uvloop,
    httptools, watchfiles, etc. can apt-install them alongside.

 -- Avalan Packaging Team <avalan@avalan.ai>  Mon, 18 May 2026 19:15:00 -0300
